---
---

<section class="problem section" aria-labelledby="problem-heading">
	<div class="container">
		<p class="eyebrow">The problem</p>
		<h2 id="problem-heading" class="problem__heading">
			You did the work weeks ago. You're still waiting on the money. Chasing
			payment has become a second job.
		</h2>
		<p class="problem__body">
			Photos are on your phone. Compliance docs are in your email. The invoice
			is on the computer at home. Every GC wants them packaged differently, and
			every rejection is another week you don't get paid.
		</p>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.problem {
		background: var(--color-surface);
		border-block: 1px solid var(--color-border);
	}

	.problem__heading {
		font-size: clamp(1.625rem, 4.5vw, 2.5rem);
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: -0.015em;
		line-height: 1.15;
		margin-top: 0.5rem;
		max-width: 28ch;
	}

	.problem__body {
		margin-top: 1.25rem;
		font-size: clamp(1.0625rem, 2.2vw, 1.25rem);
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
		max-width: 60ch;
	}
</style>
